title: Is The Lighthouse (2019) a Masterpiece?
description: Is the movie The Lighthouse (2019) a masterpiece or a pretentious mess? Is it about homosexuality? Is it better than the director’s other movie The Witch (2015)? Dr. Kirk Honda and Humberto answer these questions and more with Senior Texas Correspondent Collin.
